<item>
            <title>[FLUME-1541] Implement a SinkSelector for LoadBalancingSinkProcessor that includes failover mechanics</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLUME-1541</link>
                <project id="12311321" key="FLUME">Flume</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement a new sink selector with the following behaviors:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Round robin usage of sinks&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Temporarily removing sinks from the round robin pool when they fail&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Increasing timeout mechanics on sequential failures&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Spreading load equally over surviving sinks(current Round Robin sends all the failed sinks events to the next sink in line)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
